reviews.text: Quite nice station if you happen to want to get on or off a train, or if a train spotter and just like being near them.

A massive thank you to the staff at Fishbourne railway station for helping me lift the vat of gravy I was transporting onto the train. I managed to deliver my gravy to Eastbourne no problem and even the bingo club members were happy to have had their gravy earlier than expected.

reviews.author_name: a m e l i a c o o p e r
reviews.text: My local train station, great for getting where you need to go!
Basic train station with a ticket machine and seating.

Esta estación es en realidad poco más que un apeadero. Tiene un andén por sentido con sitio para sentarse y protegerse del mal tiempo y una máquina de billetes. Para pasar de un lado a otro carece de paso elevado. Además, tiene al lado un paso a nivel sin barreras. Cuando fuimos, los únicos trenes que paraban eran de la compañía Southern y estaban viejísimos.
